    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298300/extras/d18541b8e6798c934570a951f5492c89.avif?t=1730707299\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to learn the future of AI and AR technologies?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game lore</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You play as a middle-aged guy who leads a domestic lifestyle, has no friends, and rarely contacts people. The main character is trying to fight insomnia, and finds a solution on the Internet, AR glasses from WSALL, which, according to the company, should help him cope with sleep, but something went wrong...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298300/extras/363197d6bbc19b9f9e384df4ef6df6a5.avif?t=1730707299\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3298300/extras_big/363197d6bbc19b9f9e384df4ef6df6a5.avif?t=1730707299 width=800 height=196 /></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out the secrets of the WSALL company, why exactly will you find yourself in the center of events? How did they manage to make such an advanced artificial intelligence? Why do some users of their devices disappear? And who is behind all this?</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VHS - style</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interesting gameplay</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep lore</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A look into the future of life</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve the mysteries and get to the truth, if you succeed!</strong></p>",
